Nasdaq tackles high-speed trading in treasuries By Bradley Hope and Sarah Krouse, The Wall Street Journal 13 October 2015 Nasdaq is wading into a debate over high-speed trading in the US treasury market with a system it says can shield investors from predatory behavior.
